    2-Read the detailed description and press the "Listen " button to
    hear the artifact''s story.


    3- Press the item  button to add it to your
    progress. Watch the counter (0/6) at the top!


    4- Collect all 6 relics to
    finish your mission and unlock the final victory scene.'
